quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Ha Mīm."
  43,2,"By the Evident Scripture,"
  43,3,"indeed, We made it an Arabic Recital1, that youpl may reason."
  43,4,"And indeed, it is with Us in the Source of Scriptures, all-high, all-wise."
  43,5,"So shall We ignore reminding youpl , for having been1 an extremist people?"
  43,6,"And how many a prophet did We send to the ancients!"
  43,7,"Yet not a prophet came to them but that they used to ridicule him."
  43,8,"Thus We annihilated people more powerful than them, and so the example of the ancients has passed away."
  43,9,"And were yousg to ask them, “Who created the heavens and the earth?” They would say, “The Almighty, the All-Knowing created them.”"
  43,10,"He Who made the earth a cradle1  for youpl and traced in it ways for you, that you may be guided."